abstractProcessModelSets.name: Abstract Frame Latch
abstractProcessModelSets.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

abstractProcessModelSets.name: Theme Processor Model
abstractProcessModelSets.description: Encapsulates the details of generating and updating current programmatic style settings consumed by client application view and display processes.

transitionOperatorSets.name: Logical AND
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff all suboperations return true.

transitionOperatorSets.name: Logical NOT
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the suboperator returns false (i.e. it logically complements or inverts whatever operator it's applied to).

transitionOperatorSets.name: Logical OR
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff any suboperations return true.

transitionOperatorSets.name: Logical TRUE
transitionOperatorSets.description: Always returns Boolean true. Used typically to unilaterally transition a cell process from one step to another (e.g. always, or as a default after many other transition rules).

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Array Length Equal to Value
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the length of the array stored at OCD path equals the specified numerical value (direct or indirect).

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Boolean Flag Is Set
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated Boolean flag namespace is true.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace A ? B Value Comparison
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff operand A and B values compare using the indicated comparison operator. Note either A and/or B may be specified by value or path.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Array Empty
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace value is an array AND value.length !== 0.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Greater Than Value
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is greater than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Identical To Value
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is identical (i.e. strictly equal (===)) to the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Less Than Value
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is less than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Map Keyless
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is declared as a map in the OCD filter spec AND the OCD value is an object AND Object.key(value) !== 0.

transitionOperatorSets.name: OCD Namespace Is Truthy
transitionOperatorSets.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is truthy.

controllerActionSets.name: Frame Latch: Write
controllerActionSets.description: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.

controllerActionSets.name: OCD Boolean Flag Clear
controllerActionSets.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value false.

controllerActionSets.name: OCD Boolean Flag Set
controllerActionSets.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value true.

controllerActionSets.name: OCD Read Namespace Indirect
controllerActionSets.description: Reads and returns the value of OCD namespace via path indirection.

controllerActionSets.name: Read Theme Palette
controllerActionSets.description: Reads (and updates if necessary) the current theme output.

controllerActionSets.name: ViewThemeProcessor::Write Settings
controllerActionSets.description: Update the whole or part of the ViewThemeProcessor model's input theme settings document.

controllerActionSets.name: Write Sub-Action Response
controllerActionSets.description: A low-level utility action that dispatches a subaction returning the response to the caller and writing it also to the indicated OCD response namespace.
